                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17850112-27-off147 t17850112-27-cd149"></join> last, and putting her in corporal fear and danger of her life, and feloniously taking from her person, and against her will, one red cloth cloak, value 10 s. the property of the said William
